    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Do we really need to introduce named parameters here? I like the way the JS API client & helper are using a mix of mandatory parameters & optional parameters.\n\nRight now, most API clients are using `applicationId` and `apiKey`. I understand your point with `searchAPIKey` but the mixed camelCase naming makes it complex.\n",
