    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Do we really need to introduce named parameters here? I\n\n@redox: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/77#issuecomment-139495739\n\nWe were going to have:\n\n``` js\nvar search = instantsearch('latency', '6be0576ff61c053d5f9a3225e2a90f76', 'instant_search', {\n  numberLocale: 'fr_FR'\n}, {searchParameters});\n```\n\nSo you do not have to remember param names but you have to remember param order for 5 params.\n",
