  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'll replace with `appId` and `apiKey`, I'm ok with that as long as this is consistent with our other libraries.\n\n@redox: We'll have three mandatory arguments (appId, apiKey, indexName) and a few optional ones. Seems better to provide named parameters here, for readability.\n",
